    "description": {
      "description": "<p>Arremesso</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Um punhado de pólvora e pequenos pedaços de minério incandescente que quando arremessados fazem bastante barulho.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Uso:</span> Arremesso.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span> 5/10m.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span> [3+COG/2].</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span> animais fazem teste de Vontade com dificuldade 21 para que não fujam em pânico.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Preço:</span> 60 cobres.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Ofício:</span> Engenharia ou Armeiro N3.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo para fabricar:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 3 horas.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Materiais:</span> 1 de Pólvora<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black\">.</span></p>",
